nodes.text: "Tall" was a nickname given to a male Jenet by Leia Organa Solo. "Tall" was a member of the criminal syndicate known as the Invisible Shell. When Organa Solo visited the Pearl Island Casino on the planet Pavo Prime to negotiate with the Invisible Shell for the release of boasa statues they held, "Tall" participated in the bargaining session. He was a tall member of his species with a stooped posture.
